        <content type="html" xml:base="https://muthukamalan.github.io/posts/breath/">&lt;p&gt;When you give things space to breathe and be as they are without force, &lt;br&gt;
they fall into the right places and serve you the best.&lt;br&gt;
When we try to use our will to make things be a certain way, &lt;br&gt;
we cause more chaos than peace.&lt;br&gt;
Trust that things will fall into the perfect place and do things honestly.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</content>
        
